msContents.summary: Manuscript contains a grammatical treatise and commentary on the section of Bhaṭṭojī Dīkṣita's Siddhāntakaumudī dealing with inflected nouns (subanta). Manuscript lacks an ending and was possibly originally part of the same manuscript as Ms. Coll. 390, Item 1731.
